Raz mkstat
Call TITADI(GBOUT1,"10387") From TRTDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_MODSTL(zc) From W1HRMAT7
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_MODSTL(zc) From W1HRMAT7
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_MODSTL(zc) From W1HRMAT7
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_MODSTL(zc) From W1HRMAT7
If VALEUR="" : Call INIADI(VALEUR,"10387") From TRTDIV : Endif
